title: How To Paint: Gloomspite Gitz Rabble-Rowza
description:
Rabble-Rowzas are grots forever spoiling for a fight – and gathering mobs of mean-spirited monsters to back them up. In this video, we’ll show you how to paint up your Rabble-Rowza to be Battle Ready, then add a few extra details to take it to the next level with ease. 

If you're new to painting - check out our Citadel Colour Painting Essentials videos to learn all about it
